_Scotland" title="Template talk:Medieval Scotland"><abbr title="Discuss this template" style=";color:black;;background:none transparent;border:none;box-shadow:none;padding:0;">t</abbr></a></li><li class="nv-edit"><a href="/wiki/Special:EditPage/Template:Medieval_Scotland" title="Special:EditPage/Template:Medieval Scotland"><abbr title="Edit this template" style=";color:black;;background:none transparent;border:none;box-shadow:none;padding:0;">e</abbr></a></li></ul></div><div id="Scotland_in_the_Middle_Ages" style="font-size:114%;margin:0 4em"><a href="/wiki/Scotland_in_the_Middle_Ages" title="Scotland in the Middle Ages"><span style="color:black;">Scotland in the Middle Ages</span></a></div></th></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="navbox-group" style="width:1%">Eras</th><td class="navbox-list-with-group navbox-list navbox-odd hlist" style="width:100%;padding:0"><div style="padding:0 0.25em">
